    br
    .row
        //-2
        .col.product-image
            img.product-photos(src='../src/photos/products-photos/4spd_pro.png' alt='4SPD Control')
        .col.product-description
            h5 EVO/™ECM-4Spd-PRO (4 Speed Interface Unit)
            p.product-subheading Allows 24 Vac controls to select one of four adjustable flow indexes for an EC Motor.
            ul
                li Isolated Taps.
                li Fast or Gradual Speed Change.
                li Adjustment range is from Off to 100% of the programmed control range.
                li A fifth adjustment sets the flow index when no call is selected.
                li Pilot Pulse Enable/Disable.
                li PWM or 0-10 V output
            a.btn.btn-secondary.products(href='https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ahBTga9kY5Iwll0cx9A-ZH8_R63EL64i/view' target='_blank')
                | DATASHEET
            a.btn.btn-secondary.products(href=baseUrl + 'pro-series.html' type='button')
                | MORE ON PRO FEATURES
    br
    br
    .row
        //-3
        .col.product-image
            img.product-photos(src='../src/photos/products-photos/ACU_PRO.png' alt='4SPD Control')
        .col.product-description
            h5 EVO/™ECM-ACU-PRO (Automation Control Unit)
            p.product-subheading Allows industry standard 0-10V controllers to adjust and monitor the EC Motor.
            ul
                li Allows remote adjustment of output from 0 to 100% of programmed control range.
                li Fan flow can be factory set using manual adjust and heating can be tested without connecting a 1-10V supply.
                li Lamp indicators reference flow index.
                li During construction, heat can be used before automation is installed.
                li Air balance can be achieved before automation is installed.
                li Crystal controlled RPM accuracy.
            a.btn.btn-secondary.products(href='https://drive.google.com/file/d/1EchkIFyHA_yvEkJId7zpL-hlKiqhALsG/view' target='_blank')
                | DATASHEET
